data.description: This 3 bedroom 1 bathroom red brick home is now for sale in an awesome location! Situated on SE Madison St this home is very close to Idabel's Central Elementary School and the Super Walmart. The home features a large fenced in back yard with a garage door storage shed, a flowing floor plan from the living room to kitchen that keeps all your guest connected and entertained. The bathroom is located in the hallway and easily accessible by all residents. The property is being sold AS-IS and will need some work to bring it back to it's full enjoyment.
